reviews.text: Good place for a quick bite.

I had fish fillet set lunch today in the Hong Kong Garden shop. It was terrible, the flour coating of the fish fillet was thicker than the fish and the pasta was dried. I had never have eaten such bad food.
Eating here is pleasurable. Place is clean, not too loud even when crowded, decent food  and service quality. Price is bit high for this venue but not too bad.
Hong kong style cafe but not in local style decoration.  Standard “A,B,C” breakfast sets are available but prices are a bit expensive if compared to the typical local style ones.
Value for money

reviews.text:
獨市生意，不思進取，食物與員工服務質素每況愈下，無論早餐午餐晚餐都越嚟越差！
價錢亦不便宜，與質素不成正比，唯一可取就是環境坐得比較舒適。
午餐價錢要5-60元以上，食物種類唔算多，味道一般不算突出，由於附近餐廳小，別無選擇
